     <h1 class="title">中国禁毒网首页</h1> 
     <div class="sub_title">
      <span>来源：常识大全</span>
      <span class="time">发布时间:2016-10-11</span>
      <span>编辑:美斌&#x200d;</span>
      <span>阅读：<script src="http://fanwen.yjbys.com/plus/count.php?view=yes&amp;aid=292341&amp;mid=70" language="javascript"></script></span>
      <span class="phone"><a target="_blank" href="http://m.fanwen.yjbys.com/shenghuo/292341.html">手机版</a></span>
     </div> 
